    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring independent throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with precision plates to ensure structural longevity. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. With zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather and a flawless exterior finish, this is a turnkey, investment-grade machine for the true driving purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
