    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a single day of inclement weather. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, retaining its original factory shine. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no signs of creasing, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, binder-organized service history from authorized dealerships. The engine is whisper-quiet and the transmission shifts with seamless precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved masterpiece for the discerning buyer who demands excellence.",
